Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,426)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:55.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,420)}定格动画制作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:57.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(764,282)}定格动画制片人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:57.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(820,514)}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(756,420)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(602,390)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:01.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,432)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:03.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734,312)}客串
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:03.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,934)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.84,0:01:16.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来到海滩上跟我放松坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't y'all belly up to the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sit with me a spell?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个圣诞篝火故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a Christmas campfire story
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.01,0:01:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证你们会想听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon you'll want to hear
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个故事发生在水下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here tale takes place underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在一座乡间小镇  名叫裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In a one seahorse town called Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1404,718)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一天是平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twas the day before Christmas,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都在准备迎接圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and every boy and girl was ready for Santa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,366)}圣诞老人\N快来留在这
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了一只忙碌的松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except one busy squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.29,0:01:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在用科学辛苦工作  修修补补
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She was using her science to toil and tinker
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但她发现这次的实验有点伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but she found this experiment a bit of a thinker
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加点圣诞装饰亮片应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A touch of tinsel ought to do the trick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精灵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Elf Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪老人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sandy Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到圣诞装饰亮片了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found the tinsel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天来当我的小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for being my little elf today
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说这是用来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this all for, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.86,0:02:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个发明可以变革圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This invention will revolutionize Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打算今晚把它展示给全裤头村看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm fixing to reveal it to the whole town tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我要送给裤头村的大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be my gift to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've done it again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that ain't right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得做得再好一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta do better than that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得再来几样原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll need a few more ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才可以准时让实验就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if I want this to be ready in time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It can't be
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史赖皮  是你发出来的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slappy, did you make that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是  但我做了个新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, but I did make a new friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pa, Ma
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝迪  罗迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Randy, Rowdy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萝丝  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rosy, Granny?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不早说你还邀请了家人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me that you'd invited your family
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来裤头村过圣诞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to Bikini Bottom for the holidays?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为本来就没早说  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause she didn't, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这可是德克萨斯惊喜来访
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's a good old Texas bushwhack visit
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然得给家庭小艇钻洞才能沉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had to put a few holes in the family row boat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过能看到我们家珊迪就值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it was worth it to see our little aquatic acorn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  老妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sis
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们大老远从德克萨斯赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we came all the way from Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要来陪你这聪明小松鼠一起过圣诞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to spend Christmas with little old smartytail you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不完全是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And not at all
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为蓝迪又在当逃犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because Randy's on the lam again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is the coast clear?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道你们要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'd have known y'all were coming
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就去准备烧水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would have put the kettle on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.89,0:04:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我缓刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag me out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要帮忙吗  珊迪阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need help, Auntie Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他变蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make him turn blue
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是个什么鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the yellow snow was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个是我的工作闹钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was my work alarm
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上我一年当中最爱的班  平安夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for my favorite shift of the whole year, Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不我们一起跟过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all tag along?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'd just love to
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可想念深海里的各位朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have dearly missed all our deep sea buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,302)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  蟹堡王的客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, Krusty customers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节是不是很神奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't the holidays magical?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是想说悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you mean tragical
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁害你这么生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who upchucked in your eggnog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:21.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(706,386)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再唱一遍  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sing it again, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还得再多来点圣诞小费呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need more Christmas tips
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab, Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天都要来这吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat here every day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么什么蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something, something, Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你烂死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stink
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  干嘛非得要我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, why do I have to sing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能让我改吹竖笛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't I just play my clarinet instead?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能就是不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No can do
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拿它当圣诞柴烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm using it as a yule log today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,466)}五折
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这边这位唱圣诞颂歌的还真是喜庆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure have a festive Christmas caroler there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝他平安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bless his heart
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  奇克斯太太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mrs. Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他倒能再坚持一下  多给我赚点小费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He could stand to bring in a few more tips, though
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Matter of fact
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己也算是个歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a little something of a chanteuse myself
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我们帮你奏点乐赚点钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could strum up some tips for you, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要不用给你们付钱就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't have to pay you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  打灯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, lights, please
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节给予多多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas is a time for giving
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节收获多多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas is a time for getting
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节各种乐事都多多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas is a time for many things
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道我们爱荡秋千空翻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know we love trapeze flipping
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬大树  过上乡村生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Climbing trees and country living
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但全都比不上圣诞老人带的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But nothing beats the gifts that Santa brings
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节来得快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Christmas will come
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去得也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Christmas will go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.38,0:06:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我无法否认自己最爱这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't deny it's the day I love the most
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万物闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's aglowing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞袜也满满当当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When your stocking's overflowing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树下就放着包好的圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Santa's gifts are wrapped under the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.05,0:06:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人把礼物留给你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Santa left his gifts for you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做梦都想要今年圣诞赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm dreaming of a green Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做梦都想要今年圣诞节搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm dreaming of a bah humbug
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家今晚来我家树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on down to my tree dome tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迎接圣诞大惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a big Christmas surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.25,0:07:30.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以老妹  你老说的这个惊喜是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, sis, what exactly is this surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you keep going on about?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是要在圣诞节诈骗大伙儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or are you giving everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the old snake oil for Christmas?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这又不是耍诈  蓝迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ain't no scam, Randy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, hold your horses
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost finished
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.89,0:07:43.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要添加今天新找到的原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:43.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just add the extra ingredients I collected today
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And voila
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大功告成  而且时间刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's finally ready and just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有朋友今晚都会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All my friends will be here tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让他们今年过的圣诞节非同一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I want to make this Christmas special for em
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这次倒可以帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon we can help you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给镇上众鱼大开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,impress the fins off this town
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.12,0:08:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们的专长就是非同一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, special is our specialty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really mean it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来排练圣诞节精彩特技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got a holiday stunt spectacular to rehearse
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝大家圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说你叫我们大家过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, did you gather us here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是有什么圣诞大惊喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for some kind of big Christmas surprise?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实话  我还真有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I did
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么惊喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But whatever could it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1578,658)}圣诞佳节\N装饰品科技\N重大进展
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节装饰品科技重大进展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,breakthrough in holiday decorative technology?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来亲眼看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll just have to see for yourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.47,0:08:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为大家献上  速成圣诞树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I present to you the instant Christmas tree
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.85,0:09:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要滴上这几滴圣诞调配液  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a few drops of this here yuletide concoction, and
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家就能拥有欢乐圣诞节了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A happy holiday is all yours
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了帮我庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to help me celebrate
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.11,0:09:18.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的家人会出演全新精彩特技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my family will perform
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their newest stunt spectacular
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡桃夹子舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dance of the Nutcrackers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,同时
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a night
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.37,0:10:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好在我明天就要连放364天假了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing my 364 day vacation starts tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好的东西都要留到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saving the best for last
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回北极再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you back at the North Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把我蛋酒喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't drink all my eggnog
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,914)}潜艇雪橇
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马戏团表演
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A circus show?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.28,0:10:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样过圣诞才对嘛  你们这些派对狂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's the Christmas spirit, you party animals
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  圣诞老人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy howdy, that there's Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要让演出的最后一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon we ought to make our finale
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加倍盛大  给他好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,extra grand for him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝大家圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, one and all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这棵树马上就会变德克萨斯大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now this will be a Texas-sized tree
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.71,注释,,0,0,0,,[ Krampus：坎卜斯，反面圣诞老人\N此处用作感叹词 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, Krampus
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望他伤得没那么重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope he isn't too hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说话啊  大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,talk to me, big fella
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.88,0:12:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞奶奶  复活节兔子来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Claus, the Easter Bunny is here to see you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't good
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不知道今天什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know what day it is?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.97,0:12:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个老人家基本上是没指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That old elf is one sugarplum shy of a fruitcake
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下圣诞老人还怎么给我们送礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How is Santa gonna deliver our presents now?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他送不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪珊迪把她那棵破树种那么高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy knocked him right out of the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害他在天上撞了个正着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with her big dumb tree
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.45,0:12:53.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我才不相信树
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:53.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why I don't trust trees
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.50,0:12:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是没有礼物  圣诞节还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what's the point of having Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without any presents?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱就是说  你把圣诞节给毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, like, totally ruined Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会有事的  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码圣诞老人还很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least Santa's having a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对才刚要开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The party's just getting started
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是当晚  小镇陷入了寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so the town went quiet that night
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居民们一个接一个地熄灯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One by one, they put out their lights
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.91,0:13:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩也不是  乐也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No fun to be had, no joy to be doing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.79,0:13:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能呜呜咽咽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just the soft, sad sounds of gentle boohooing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本可吃着南瓜派
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should be eating pumpkin pie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但却让全城都悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But instead I made the whole town cry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我犯了什么过错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the world was I doing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节完全覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now Christmas is ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在圣诞多忧苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the Christmas blues
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉自己格格不入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel like I just don't belong
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.29,0:14:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多希望能够唱出幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish that I could sing a happy song
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只好在这坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll just sit here and stew
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不停地哀泣痛哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And keep aweeping boohoo
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.51,0:14:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在圣诞多忧苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the Christmas blues
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能有意外转机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only some unexpected fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能从天而降就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would just appear from above
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我们发现啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what we found
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们说  全都是圣诞老人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all Santa's gifts, I tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以留着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we keep em?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没有  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有意外转机从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An unexpected fortune just appeared from above
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold your seahorses, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了礼物也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't no use having gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人现在都送不了礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if Santa can't deliver them
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人还在发病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's still indisposed
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以圣诞节一样还是毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meaning Christmas is still ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们也不是第一年没有过圣诞老人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ain't the first time we had a year without Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得1874年精灵大罢工那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember the Great Elf Strike of 1874
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那年圣诞  我们整座小镇都很忧苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our whole town was real blue that Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们还是尽力挺了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we made the most of it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正没圣诞老人也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No Santa, no problem
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们奇克斯家联手  自己交换礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We Cheeks banded together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and exchanged gifts all on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇克斯家族绝不退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The family Cheeks ain't quitters
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前不退缩  现在也不会退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We weren't then, and we ain't now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Granny's right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起为圣诞老人而战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do this for Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,划啊划啊划小船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Row, row, row your boat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来顺流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gently down the stream
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾  驾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giddyap, giddyap
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lookie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056,360)}火箭发射
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们送彩蛋好运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck delivering those Easter eggs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝迪来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Randy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罗迪和萝丝来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Rowdy and Rosy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给妈  交给爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On Ma, on Pa
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给奶奶  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on Granny, and
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱们送礼就得来点音乐  振奋精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we need a little
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,musical motivation to get this job done
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节给予多多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas is a time for giving
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节收获多多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas is a time for getting
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节各种乐事都多多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas is a time for many things
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道我们爱欢唱颂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know we like carol singing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四处溜冰  捉捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Skating round and jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但全都比不上我们疯狂大家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But nothing beats our nutty family
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送礼表示我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giving gifts means I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是不如来度过好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not like spending time so happily
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞佳节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At Christmas time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为需要的东西样样全都有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause we got everything we'll ever need
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样样全都有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll ever need
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我们相隔千里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We may be miles apart
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你们知道在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you know in my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这坚果与家族大树永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This nut don't fall far from the family tree
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家就位  马上出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Places, y'all, and here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(848,752)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转啊转啊  往右拐弯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Round and round and turn to the right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平安夜来  应该没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas Eve, it should be bright
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王里  一片荒凉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab looks mighty low
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  与我共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob, let's do-si-do
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so blue
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel the same
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No Christmas gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad, this is lame
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙放心  不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, folks, don't worry, and don't you fear
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞礼物  马上送到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your Christmas gifts will soon be here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你们有事要先做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there is something you must do
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则圣诞老人就不来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or old Saint Nick won't visit you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螃蟹鲸鱼  得先睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good crabs and whales should be asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数羊入眠  才有礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No gifts unless you're counting sheep
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,互相致意  然后继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So bow to your partner, go on ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,砸昏自己  快快上床
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock yourself out and go to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向左舞动  如蓝鸟飞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now allemande left and fly like a bluebird
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝迪奶奶去章鱼哥家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Randy and Granny to the house of Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踮起脚尖  偷偷送礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walk on your tiptoes, give him his gift
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵醒他  要快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't wake him up, now, better be swift
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么动静  我的老天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what's that noise, holy mackerel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉这声音很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dagnabbit, that sound ain't natural
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚肯定没办法安静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure ain't no silent night
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竖笛噪音  吵吵闹闹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squeaks and honks and clarinet squawks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塞圣诞袜  马上消停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop that noise with Christmas socks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来是  罗迪萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Rowdy's next and Rosie too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快跳去派大星家中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To Patrick Star's we skip to my Lou
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷偷行动  别发声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, sneak, sneak, don't make a squeak
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物好大  漏出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a big old gift, and it's starting to leak
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's sand, sand
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来不及了  快上椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too late now, better hop on a chair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这圣诞礼物非常离奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Christmas gift is mighty quirky
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  派大星应该爱火鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, I think Pat likes turkey
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们  干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, kids, you're doing fine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一站是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next stop is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're out of time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.97,0:19:25.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没办法把裤头村的礼物送完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll never finish delivering
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all these gifts to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aunt Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把你做的调配液带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We brought along that concoction you made
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能会有用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it'll help
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It ain't gonna work
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞欢乐已经快耗尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's running short on Christmas cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以补救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we can fix that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  家人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right, family?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.61,0:19:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节来得快  去得也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas will come, and Christmas will go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们互相表示爱意  那些日子最长久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What stays are the days that we say I love you so
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万物闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's a-glowing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞袜也满满当当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when your stocking's overflowing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树下就放着包好的圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Santa's gifts are wrapped under the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.42,0:20:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有家人在一起  礼物变得多么美好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gifts are so much better when your family is together
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陆地海里都完全无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whether it's on land or in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.85,0:20:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,和你共度佳节  正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A holiday with you is right for me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,及时送完礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We made it just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得跟圣诞老人报个喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to tell Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是个什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们拯救了圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We saved Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我们是先毁了圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, we ruined Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们之后又救回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then we saved it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.09,0:20:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只记得先前有棵特别大的圣诞树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The last thing I remember was a big Christmas tree
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你就摔了个屁股着地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you fell on your rumpumpumpum
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We thought you was dead
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你现在没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you're fine now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还把你圣诞礼物都送完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we took care of your Christmas presents
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我不在淘气坏孩子名单上了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This means I'm off the naughty list, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们修好了我雪橇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fixed my sleigh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们值得我圣诞老人送上特别大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You all deserve special presents from Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.99,0:21:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很感谢  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过今年圣诞想要的东西我已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I already got what I wanted for Christmas this year
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们并不需要高大上的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We never needed nothing fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.13,0:21:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁还要什么礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs presents, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱就是说  我们很感谢能收到礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're, like, totally grateful for ours
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们咋知道是我们送的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you know it was us?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物上面沾了点松鼠毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we found a little squirrel fur on our gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还整晚在房顶上唱约德尔调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were also yodeling on our rooftops all night
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然如此  还是要谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we all thank you nonetheless
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No need to thank us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点在于  大家能欢聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's important is that we're all together
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们还有这棵大树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we also got this big old tree
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这树可是珊迪给咱改造的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy got it souped up for us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可以拿它当新家住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Figured y'all could use it as a new house
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we come
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫圣诞礼物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that is a Christmas present
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然能见到你们是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seeing y'all was great
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是免费东西最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but nothing beats free stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.51,0:22:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把这棵德克萨斯大小的树
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get this Texas-sized tree
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,物归原位  德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back where it belongs, Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.81,0:22:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以上就是一家疯狂松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that is the story of how a family of nutty squirrels
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先是毁了  接着又拯救圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ruined and then saved Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么一个海底故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.41,0:22:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己都难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hardly believe it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝大家圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You all come back, now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.96,0:22:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,910)}祝大家佳节愉快
